"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-high-jumper-yaroslava-mahuchikh-wins-ukraines-first-individual-gold-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Sunday night at Stade de France, and Yaroslava Mahuchikh is here but not here.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 95, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 48, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 73, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaroslava_Mahuchikh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yaroslava Mahuchikh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaroslava_Mahuchikh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaroslava_Mahuchikh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other end of the stadium, 12 men are trying to medal in the hammer throw; on the track, runners in three events are trying to advance to the finals; in Mahuchikh\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hometown, Ukrainian troops are trying to save their country.\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.996808673345698, \"rank\": 0.00290943703374246, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not possible to focus only on track, to high jump,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she will say later, when she is asked if she can clear her mind when she competes.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOur families in Ukraine \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 we have friends who are fighting \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999992007036337, \"rank\": 7.560646151534955e-07, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot forget about this.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember, always.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  The high jump bar is set at 1.86 meters to start.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In early July, Mahuchikhbroke the 37-year-old world record, jumping 2.10 meters.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day, Russia bombed five Ukrainian cities, including Dnipro, where Mahuchikh grew up.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999708848340861, \"rank\": 2.695273378934969e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 763, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.996808673345698, \"rank\": 0.00290943703374246, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\", \"score\": 0.9979062882217643, \"rank\": 0.002098088463605095, \"text\": \"Dnipro\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mahuchikh knows she can jump higher than 1.86 meters, so she passes on this round.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bombs killed at least 31 people.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mahuchikh makes her first jump, at 1.91 meters, and clears the bar on her first attempt.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the bombs hit a children\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hospital.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bar is raised to 1.95 meters.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cA lot of rocket attacks to my city,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mahuchikh will say later.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three jumpers fail to clear 1.95; eight remain.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe had a lot of alarms and a lot of explosions in my region,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bar is raised to 1.98 meters.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe fight to represent our country, and to show people we are strong,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mahuchikh will say.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Six jumpers fail to clear 1.98; only Mahuchikh and Australia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Nicola Olyslagers remain.\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Between jumps, Olyslagers opens her journal and writes her thoughts.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Between jumps, Mahuchikhclimbs in a sleeping bagto calm her mind..\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bar is raised to 2.0 meters.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Russia invaded, Maruchikh packed belongings in her car and fled Ukraine, and now she is not there but she is there.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999708848340861, \"rank\": 2.695273378934969e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1767, \"end\": 1774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999992007036337, \"rank\": 7.560646151534955e-07, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maruchikh clears 2.0 meters on her first attempt; Olyslagers knocks the bar down on her first two.\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four days ago, there were reports of explosions in Dnipro.\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1969, \"end\": 1975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\", \"score\": 0.9979062882217643, \"rank\": 0.002098088463605095, \"text\": \"Dnipro\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clap \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 clap \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6  Olyslagers puts her hands together to get the crowd going.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the fans at Stade de France who showed up primarily for the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 100-meter final, Olyslagers is a revelation.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before each jump, she looks like a giggly kid who doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t think she can blow out all the candles on her birthday cake.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She talks to herself and doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t care how it looks; everybody in the stadium can see her lips move on the big screens.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She grins after each jump, whether she was successful or not, and she has a smile as wide as the sea.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clap \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 clap \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6  On her third attempt, Olyslagers clears 2.0.\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t happen often, but it has already happened here: Two Ukrainains and two Australians have medaled in this event.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ukraine\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Iryna Gerashchenko and Australia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Eleanor Patterson share bronze.\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Herashchenko\", \"score\": 0.9999934691931667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gerashchenko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Herashchenko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Herashchenko\"}, {\"begin\": 2757, \"end\": 2774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eleanor_Patterson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eleanor Patterson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eleanor_Patterson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eleanor_Patterson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Olyslagers and Ukraine\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Mahuchikh will get gold and silver, in some order.\\u00c2  The bar is raised to 2.02 meters.\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olyslagers fails to clear it on her first two attempts.\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But so does Mahuchikh.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olyslagers needs to succeed on her third attempt to have a chance at gold; otherwise, Mahuchikh will win because she has needed fewer attempts to get here.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI want to say that of course we won medals for our Ukrainian people and our defenders,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mahuchikh will say later.\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3207, \"end\": 3216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.996808673345698, \"rank\": 0.00290943703374246, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olyslagers lifts off.\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe want peace,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Mahuchikh will say.\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olyslagers knocks the bar over.\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yaroslava Mahuchikh has won Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3368, \"end\": 3387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaroslava_Mahuchikh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yaroslava Mahuchikh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaroslava_Mahuchikh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaroslava_Mahuchikh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other side of Stade de France, Mykhaylo Kokhan, another native of Dnipro, has taken bronze in the hammer throw.\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3431, \"end\": 3446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 3483, \"end\": 3489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\", \"score\": 0.9979062882217643, \"rank\": 0.002098088463605095, \"text\": \"Dnipro\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dnipro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mahuchikh, Kokhan and Gerashchenko carry the Ukraine flag around the stadium to celebrate.\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3551, \"end\": 3563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Herashchenko\", \"score\": 0.9999934691931667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gerashchenko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Herashchenko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volodymyr_Herashchenko\"}, {\"begin\": 3574, \"end\": 3581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999992007036337, \"rank\": 7.560646151534955e-07, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joy takes many forms, and we need them all.\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the medalists\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 press conference after the high jump, two Australians and two Ukrainians smile and compliment each other and try to make the most of their time behind microphones.\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3747, \"end\": 3757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.7119241638775482, \"rank\": 0.4046439926313815, \"text\": \"Ukrainians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olyslagers encourages kids to be patient as they chase their dreams.\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manuchikh urges people to remember her country.\\u00c2  The silver medalist says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cGive yourself at least 10 years.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The gold medalist says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSometimes I forget that I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m only 22.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Michael Rosenberg is a senior writer for Sports Illustrated, covering any and all sports.\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 4192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4103, \"end\": 4120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Rosenberg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0494387102779986e-17, \"text\": \"Michael Rosenberg\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Rosenberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Rosenberg\"}, {\"begin\": 4144, \"end\": 4162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6367764522652887e-21, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He writes columns, profiles and investigative stories and has covered almost every major sporting event.\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He joined SI in 2012 after working at the Detroit Free Press for 13 years, eight of them as a columnist.\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4340, \"end\": 4358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Detroit_Free_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Detroit Free Press\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Detroit_Free_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Detroit_Free_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rosenberg is the author of \\\"War As They Knew It: Woody Hayes, Bo Schembechler and America in a Time of Unrest.\\\"\", \"from\": 4403, \"to\": 4514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4403, \"end\": 4412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julius_and_Ethel_Rosenberg\", \"score\": 0.9940828631141934, \"rank\": 0.00595235671917819, \"text\": \"Rosenberg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julius_and_Ethel_Rosenberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julius_and_Ethel_Rosenberg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several of his stories also have been published in collections of the year's best sportswriting.\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is married with three children.\", \"from\": 4612, \"to\": 4646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow rosenberg_mike  \\u00c2\\u00a9 2025ABG-SI LLC- SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 4773, \"to\": 4849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Sports Illustrated or its affiliates, licensees and related brands.\", \"from\": 4850, \"to\": 5044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4977, \"end\": 4995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6367764522652887e-21, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, crisis counseling and referral services can be accessed by calling 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 5134, \"to\": 5266, \"entities\": []}]}"